column2: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri where { <A> dbo:musicalArtist ?x . ?x dbp:associatedActs ?uri }

column1: With which musical artist is the music group which sung <A> related to ?
column2: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri where { <A> dbo:musicalArtist ?x . ?x dbo:associatedMusicalArtist ?uri }

column1: With which musical artist is the producer of <A> associated ?
column2: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri where { <A> dbo:producer ?x . ?x dbp:associatedActs ?uri . ?x a dbo:MusicalArtist }
